      "content": "that's a good start. can u go deeper into the part about 'dismantling structural barriers'? i want to argue that the current idea of meritocracy is basically just a way to justify why some people stay poor while others stay rich. how can i frame meritocracy as being fundamentally incompatible with racial equity in my essay?",
